+- Automated backup strategy
+- WebSocket optimization
+- Container auto-scaling
+
+### 10.2 Migration Path
+- Phase 2: Add authentication if needed
+- Phase 3: External access via VPN
+- Phase 4: Kubernetes migration for scale
